title: Albert King - 1983 - Crosscut Saw (Albert King In San Francisco)
description:
Albert King - 1983 - Crosscut Saw (Albert King In San Francisco) (1992)

Crosscut Saw reissues Albert King's 1983 album San Francisco '83 (a studio album, not a live one), adding two previously unreleased cuts. His first new release in five years, it wasn't one of King's better records -- but it did represent a return to a basic five-piece sound, an improvement upon his over-produced outings of the late '70s. (AllMusic)
